{
  "texts": [
    "Training is done for a maximum of 8 epochs for all GLUE data sets except SST-2 for which we allocate maximum 3 epochs.",
    "We set an initial learning rate of 5e -4 for QNLI & MNLI, and 1e -3 for other GLUE data sets.",
    "We use rank r = 8 for the low rank matrices A, B unless mentioned otherwise.",
    "We choose gradient scaling hyper-parameter γ = 1 for SST-2 and γ = 2 for all other data sets.",
    "Following [16], we use the fine-tuned MNLI checkpoint to initialize the model weights for experiments on small data sets such as RTE and MRPC."
  ]
}